description: Memphis style and taste are on the move in the heart of Michigan! Scott's Pig Roast is bringing BBQ like you've never tasted in the whole Midwest. The perfect truck for any occasion, Scott's Pork Roast will make a menu to suit you and cook it in that amazing Memphis BBQ style. So if you're looking for some real flavor made right, Scott's Pig Roast is the truck for you!
name: Scott's Pig Roast
